 [7] King&#39;s Room<br>
 [8] Wizard&#39;s Vale<br>
 [9] Palantir Chamber <br>
<br>
Free Peoples [30]<br>
  From the Starter:<br>
    Brego x1<br>
    Éomer, Sister Son of Théoden x1<br>
